b3 {exposes the long diagonal, so it makes sense to play} exd4 ({Instead,} 
18... Rc8 19. Rb1 c6 20. a4 Qc7 21. Bd3 $14 {was passive for Black in Salem,A
- Flores Rios,M Tromso 2014}) 19. cxd4 c5 20. d5 a5 21. Rb1 (21. Bc3 b4 22. Bb2
Ba6 23. Qf4 Qe7 $132 {also offers Black plenty of play on the queenside.}) ({
Pointless is} 21. Bd3 Ba6 22. a4 b4 23. Bxa6 Rxa6 24. Qc4 Ra8 $15 {the poor
location of the d2-bishop doesn't allow White to set-up a blockade.}) 21... b4
22. Bd3 a4 23. a3 axb3 24. axb4 Rc8 $1 {[%eval -32767,0] Black had excellent
